author: Matt Walsh
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, Democrats continue to rally around Kilmar Abrego Garcia. He's a bad person, none of these people would want him in their neighborhood, but they can't drop him now. They're in too deep. We'll discuss. Also, Cracker Barrel tries to clean up the PR mess they've created for themselves. Southwest Airlines announces that fat people will have to pay for a second seat if they're too bulbous to fit into one. And Donald Trump makes a move to stop people from desecrating the American flag.
